1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/david-lynch@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>已故导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-lynch">戴维·林奇（David Lynch）</a>的家人在报道中发表了有关电影制片人纪念和葬礼服务的详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/david-lynch-obituary-twin-peaks-3829834">大卫·林奇（David Lynch） -  1946-2025：一个真正有远见的人，他重新发明了电影</a></strong></li></ul><p>林奇（Lynch）的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-dies-aged-78-3829681">死是他的家人在本月初（1月16日）在社交媒体上宣布的</a>- 他现年78岁。林奇（Lynch），他因穆尔霍兰<em>（Mulholland Drive）</em> ，<em>蓝色天鹅绒（Blue Velvet）</em>和标志性电视连续剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/twin-peaks"><em>Twin Peaks</em></a>等电影而闻名，他去年透露了他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynchs-health-problems-mean-he-can-no-longer-direct-in-person-3781105">肺气肿诊断</a>。这是由于他一生中吸烟引起的。 11月，他透露他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-now-requires-supplemental-oxygen-to-walk-its-a-big-price-to-pay-3812940">需要补充氧气行走</a>。</p><p>昨晚，林奇（Lynch）的家人上了Facebook谴责一份报告，声称已故电影偶像的葬礼将于1月28日在洛杉矶的Wilshire Ebell剧院举行，并将包括“传统追悼会”。该报告还声称，林奇（Lynch）的密友和合作者像凯尔·麦克拉克兰（Kyle Maclachlan）和劳拉·德恩（Laura Dern）将在服务中出席，并“预计会提供悼词”，并补充说，“只有家庭成员才会为家庭成员进行私人埋葬仪式”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3829858" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829858" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829858" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Lynch-2017.jpg" alt="大卫·林奇（David Lynch）的怪异Playstation广告正在传播" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Lynch-2017.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Lynch-2017-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Lynch-2017-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Lynch-2017-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Lynch-2017-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Lynch-2017-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829858" class="wp-caption-text">大卫·林奇（David Lynch）在2017年。信贷：Stefania d&#39;Alessandro/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>林奇（Lynch）的家人写道，驳回了报告：“希望大卫·林奇（David Lynch）在路上有某种纪念馆，但现在1月28日或其他任何时候都没有葬礼或任何事情。我为人们为此而飞来飞去，我觉得有人发布这种废话是如此错误。这很伤心。请向任何发布这些谎言的人投诉。”</p><p>他的家人补充说：“另外，没有举行葬礼，所以这个故事也是一堆谎言。不要相信您阅读的所有内容！抱怨那些发布谎言的人只是为了吸引观众。真的很可悲。”</p><p>您可以看到下面的完整帖子，包括多次在报告的屏幕上写的“胡说八道”一词。” </p><div id="fb-root"></div><p><script async="1" defer="1" crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v22.0"></script></p><div class="fb-post" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/davidlynchofficial/posts/pfbid02yoAdAg1QNiUvBJUyypKW9Dtaj8VrNdUmpnA4VKJoZ3cy9WArrrPQkt8vBorWJSiNl" data-width="696"><blockquote cite="https://graph.facebook.com/100044613211418/posts/1183976236432806/" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><p>请传播这个词……希望大卫·林奇（David Lynch）在路上有某种纪念馆，但现在在那里……</p><p> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/davidlynchofficial">David Lynch</a>发表于<a href="https://graph.facebook.com/100044613211418/posts/1183976236432806/">2025年1月23日，星期四</a></p></blockquote></div><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-dies-aged-78-3829681">林奇（Lynch）于1月15日去世</a>后，第二天他的家人在他的Facebook页面上写道：“令人遗憾的是，我们，他的家人宣布男人和艺术家大卫·林奇（David Lynch）的去世。目前，我们将不胜感激。</p><p> “现在他不再与我们在一起，世界上有一个大漏洞。但是，正如他会说的那样，“请关注甜甜圈，而不是在孔上”。这是美好的一天，一路有金色的阳光和蓝天。”</p><p>自林奇（Lynch）逝世以来，娱乐行业的致敬涌入。传奇导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/steven-spielberg-pays-tribute-to-david-lynch-an-original-and-unique-voice-3829853">史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格（Steven Spielberg）</a>将他描述为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/steven-spielberg-pays-tribute-to-david-lynch-an-original-and-unique-voice-3829853">“原始而独特的声音”</a> ，回想起他们在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-fabelmans-review-steven-spielberg-3387525"><em>法布尔曼斯（Fabelmans）</em></a>上的作品。 Netflix联合首席执行官Ted Sarandos透露，林奇（Lynch）正在为流媒体计划<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-was-planning-a-netflix-show-with-mystery-and-risks-3830382">“充满神秘和风险”</a>的新系列。</p><p>在其他向林奇致敬的名人中，还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/laura-dern-david-lynch-birthday-tribute-3830806">劳拉·德恩（Laura Dern）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/edgar-wright">埃德加·赖特（Edgar Wright）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-gunn">詹姆斯·冈恩（James Gunn）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hugh-jackman">休·杰克曼（Hugh Jackman）</a> ，比利·科根<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">（Billy Corgan</a> ）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/questlove">Questlove</a> -<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-dies-aged-78-3829681">请参见更多的致敬</a>。</p><p>林奇（Lynch）的粉丝也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-fans-celebrate-late-director-on-his-79th-birthday-long-live-the-greatest-3830502">很快向他致敬</a>，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-fans-hold-worldwide-group-meditation-to-honour-late-directors-legacy-3830534">一些人举行了“全球冥想”。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynchs-family-slam-bullshit-reports-of-memorial-service-its-hurtful-3831619">大卫·林奇（David Lynch）的家庭大满贯“胡说八道”的追悼会报告：“这是伤害”的</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 M. Night Shyamalan否认审判开始复制“仆人”的想法：“这项指控与我所做的一切完全相反” https://www.nme.com/news/film/m-night-shyamalan-denies-copying-idea-for-servant-servant-servant-as-benial-begins-berin-begins-this-accusation-is-cuscusation-is-cuscusation-is-the-the-the-the-the-the-ex-ex-ex-expopose一切i-i-do-do-3831598？一切，我做Emma WilkesFri, 24 Jan 2025 01:34:09 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3831598 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Francesca Gregorini声称Shyamalan应对她2013年的电影《关于伊曼纽尔的真相》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/m-night-shyamalan-denies-copying-idea-for-servant-as-trial-begins-this-accusation-is-the-exact-opposite-of-everything-i-do-3831598">M. Night Shyamalan帖子否认在审判开始时否认复制“仆人”的想法：“这一指控与我所做的一切完全相反”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/m-night-shyamalan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> M. Night Shyamalan M.否认在他的pla窃审判开始时，否认了为<em>仆人</em>复制这个想法。</p><p>导演昨天（1月22日）作证说，他和他的合作者没有复制一部由弗朗切斯卡·格雷戈里尼（Francesca Gregorini）执导的关于妄想母亲和她的婴儿娃娃的<em>关于伊曼纽尔的真相</em>。她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/m-night-shyamalan-accused-of-copying-2013-thriller-in-plagiarism-lawsuit-2598198">在2020年对Shyamalan提起诉讼，</a>不久之后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple+电视</a>节目首次亮相。</p><p>格雷戈里尼（Gregorini）的电影描绘了一个保姆，他喂养了母亲对娃娃是真实的妄想。 Shyamalan在加利福尼亚州里弗赛德的联邦审判期间对<a href="https://variety.com/2025/film/news/m-night-shyamalan-servant-testimony-copyright-trial-apple-1236282282/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>陪审团</em></a>说，版权纠纷显然是“ 100％，误解”。</p><p> Shyamalan说：“这一指控与我所做的一切以及我试图代表的一切都相反。”当被问及他是否从电影中复制任何东西时，他说：“绝对不是。” </p><figure id="attachment_3780530" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3780530" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3780530" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Trap-director-M-Night-Shyamalan-.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Trap-director-M-Night-Shyamalan-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Trap-director-M-Night-Shyamalan--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Trap-director-M-Night-Shyamalan--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Trap-director-M-Night-Shyamalan--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Trap-director-M-Night-Shyamalan--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Trap-director-M-Night-Shyamalan--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3780530" class="wp-caption-text">陷阱导演M Night Shyamalan。图片来源：盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>在上周四（1月16日）的证词中，格雷戈里尼说，当她第一次见到<em>仆人的预告片时，</em>她感到“震惊”，她声称这是“我电影的跳动和骨骼”，甚至据说却镜子镜子了。</p><p>她说：“我简直不敢相信我所看到的。” “我可以看到他们基本上拍了我的电影，然后……重做。”</p><p>后来，她说：“我意识到，在采取诉讼时，我会为自己而战，也是为了我自己所发生的事情，但对于其他人，无论出于何种原因，我都无法在法庭上度过一天。您不能接受别人的工作，重新利用它，将其称为自己，也不会给那些制造的人提供信用或赔偿。”</p><p> Shyamalan在证词中在周三作证说，他直到本月初才看过Gregorini的电影。当他观看时，他说他发现“其中的一切都来自其他电影。”</p><p> “我不拥有它们。任何人都可以做这些照片，”他说。 “从希区柯克和库布里克面前，我们彼此之间的学习范围很长。他们没有发明它。它在他们面前，然后继续前进。”</p><p><em>仆人的</em>概念是由作家托尼·巴斯加洛普（Tony Basgallop）创建的，他上周作证说，他于2005年开始研究这个想法。他说他借鉴了自己的生活经历，也从未见过或听说过格雷戈里尼的电影，直到提起诉讼。 </p><figure id="attachment_3393546" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3393546" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3393546" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/M_Night_Shyamalan_Getty.jpg" alt="Shyamalan" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/M_Night_Shyamalan_Getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/M_Night_Shyamalan_Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/M_Night_Shyamalan_Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/M_Night_Shyamalan_Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/M_Night_Shyamalan_Getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/M_Night_Shyamalan_Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3393546" class="wp-caption-text"> M. Night Shyamalan在英国特别放映伦敦的“敲门机舱”。图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>格雷戈里尼的律师帕特里克·阿伦兹（Patrick Arenz）观察到，娃娃元素要到2016年才进入剧本。当时，竞技场指出，Basgallop当时在专业和财务上都在挣扎，这表明娃娃元素帮助脚本出售和出售和生产 - 它来自<em>伊曼纽尔</em>。</p><p>阿内兹（Arenz）试图让Shyamalan承认电影和演出之间的一系列相似之处。在各个方面，Shyamalan提供了区别作品的其他背景，以至于Arenz说他要“切线”，并指示他直接回答问题。</p><p>阿纳兹（Arenz）指出，<em>仆人</em>的母亲角色直到该系列的结构几乎与电影结构类似，才发现她的孩子发生了什么。</p><p> Shyamalan说：“谜团 - 耶利哥发生了什么 - 我想拯救。” “这是一个重要的引擎。”</p><p>该案预计将在本周晚些时候向陪审团前往陪审团。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/m-night-shyamalan-denies-copying-idea-for-servant-as-trial-begins-this-accusation-is-the-exact-opposite-of-everything-i-do-3831598">M. Night Shyamalan帖子否认在审判开始时否认复制“仆人”的想法：“这一指控与我所做的一切完全相反”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
本周谁在“叛徒”上被杀？ https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-3-who-was-kill-3827323?utm_source=rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = the-campaign = the-the = the-campaign = the-the-the-the-the-traitors-traitors-season-3-who-who-was-was-killAdam Starkey Thu, 23 Jan 2025 22:00:40 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3827323 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克劳迪娅·温克尔曼（Claudia Winkleman）与“叛徒”的第三场选手" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>剧透第三季</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-3-who-was-killed-3827323">本周在“叛徒”上被杀害的哨所？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克劳迪娅·温克尔曼（Claudia Winkleman）与“叛徒”的第三场选手" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>经过两个赛季和世界各地的其他几个版本，<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-traitors"><em>叛徒</em></a>仍然是电视上最受关注的真人秀之一。</p><p>由克劳迪娅·温克尔曼（Claudia Winkleman）主持，第三季看到25名参赛者在苏格兰高地的一座城堡中争夺价值高达12万英镑的奖金。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/best-tv-shows-2025-stranger-things-bear-andor-wednesday-3826471">20个大型电视节目在2025年期待</a></strong></li></ul><p>在城堡中，选出几名参赛者是“叛徒”，他们必须掩盖自己的身份并消除“忠实者”以要求获得奖项。但是，如果忠实的人设法通过每日圆桌会议驱逐所有叛徒，那么所有幸存的参赛者都将赢得现金奖。</p><p>英国广播公司（BBC）去年将演出续签了第四季，还播放了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-uk-celebrity-edition-announced-3786092">九集名人版</a>。</p><h2>谁在第一周离开了<em>叛徒</em>第3季？</h2><p>开幕剧集介绍了所有25名参赛者，尽管他们甚至在踏入城堡之前就进行了火车车辆的转折。三名参赛者不得不提名自己离开火车，不知道结果会是什么。</p><p>选择离开火车的参赛者是亚历山大·龙蒂（Alexander Dragonetti），福齐·法西尔（Fozia Fasil）和杰克·马林纳·布朗（Jack Marriner-Brown），他们都暂时从比赛中撤离。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：尹吕（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827330" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827330" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827330" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin.jpg" alt="叛乱者在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827330" class="wp-caption-text"> YinLü在“叛徒”中：BBC和Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>由于叛徒受到了传播博士的怀疑和智力的威胁，尹吕是第三季中第一位被谋杀的参赛者。</p><p><strong>放逐：内森·希德（Nathan Khider）（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827328" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827328" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827328" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg" alt="内森在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827328" class="wp-caption-text">内森（Nathan）在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管在圆桌会议上对叛徒琳达感到怀疑，但八名球员投票赞成驱逐39年历史的房地产顾问内森（Nathan）。该决定基于他安静的举止之外的证据很少。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：基思·斯图尔特（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827333" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827333" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827333" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg" alt="基思在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827333" class="wp-caption-text">基思在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>窗户清洁工基思（Keith）被认为是一个坚强而讨人喜欢的角色，成为叛徒谋杀的第二个人。</p><p><strong>放逐：Elen Wyn（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827334" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827334" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827334" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg" alt="叛徒的埃伦" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827334" class="wp-caption-text">埃伦（Elen</figcaption></figure><p>在被其他球员挂钩后，加上她相信大多数叛徒将是“坚强的女性”之后，翻译者埃伦（Elen）被淘汰了。</p><p>她告诉<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/crrw4d1lxygo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>：“一旦您的名字出现在那里，就很难拯救自己。”</p><p><strong>放逐：Armani Gouveia（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827329" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827329" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827329" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg" alt="叛徒阿玛尼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827329" class="wp-caption-text">阿玛尼（Armani）是第三季中第一个离开的叛徒：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>球员们在第三集中设法消除了他们的第一个叛徒，因为阿玛尼的勇气和指挥态度迅速与她作战。她自己的姐姐迈亚·古维亚（Maia Gouveia）承认对自己的行为有怀疑，她的命运被封锁了。</p><h2>谁在第二周离开？</h2><p>在情节的第二周开始时，以前淘汰了选手亚历山大·龙妮蒂，福齐亚·法西尔和杰克·马里纳·布朗，被带回了一个挑战，使他们挂在森林中的笼子里。</p><p>玩家只能节省三名悬而未决的参赛者中的两名，然后从这一点开始就加入了比赛。在提出令人信服的争论之后，亚历山大和弗齐亚被球员救出，而出生于约克郡的市场商人<strong>杰克被送回家</strong>。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：Maia Gouveia（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827331" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827331" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827331" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia.jpg" alt="迈亚在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827331" class="wp-caption-text"> Maia在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在她的姐姐在最后一个圆桌会议上被驱逐出境之后，叛徒选择谋杀玛雅，以取出可能是强大的对手。她的去世还对弗雷迪（Freddie）引起了怀疑，弗雷迪（Freddie）以前在上一场圆桌会议上以她为目标。</p><p><strong>放逐：卡西姆·艾哈迈德（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827327" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827327" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827327" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg" alt="叛徒的卡西姆" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827327" class="wp-caption-text"> Kasim被驱逐出每个人的沮丧：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>这是不幸的必然性，卡西姆被从小组中被驱逐出来，因为他只是太好了，而且 - 至少在杰克的脑海中 - 因为他是一名医生。阿玛尼（Armani）是在莫名其妙地为他保证他之后，在上一个圆桌会议上封锁了命运的人，其他球员说服他也是叛徒。</p><p><strong>放逐：泰勒·史密斯（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827710" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827710" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827710" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new.jpg" alt="泰勒叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827710" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管弗雷迪（Freddie）发热量，但当莱昂（Leon）和莱恩（Leanne）开始怀疑他们内心圈子中的某人时，潮汐在圆桌会议上与29岁的理发师泰勒（Tyler）脱颖而出。他的离开引起了利维（Livi）的特别激动的反应，利维（Livi）因决定而流泪。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：Livi Deane（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3828057" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828057" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828057" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors.jpg" alt="利维叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828057" class="wp-caption-text"> Livi在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>为了将弗雷迪（Freddie）进一步加入射击线，叛徒决定杀死26岁的美容师和模特丽维（Livi）在圆桌会议上的情感爆发之后。</p><p><strong>放逐：丹·伯德（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3828064" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828064" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828064" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors.jpg" alt="丹在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828064" class="wp-caption-text">丹在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管在剧集之前没有在任何人的雷达上，但丹在挑战期间的谎言还是在圆桌会议上撤消了他。 Leanne和Minah都面临着他的面对面，他们将焦点放在了他的隐藏真理上。</p><h2>谁在第三周离开？</h2><p>第三周的第一次谋杀案有一个转折。叛徒挑选了四名参赛者玩一场名为“死亡比赛”的纸牌游戏，其失败者将被谋杀。</p><p> Leon，Alexander，Fosia和Anna被选为比赛。每轮的获胜者都免于谋杀。</p><p>其余的球员在下一个任务中发现了比赛的结果，他们在棺材里找到了幸存的球员。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：Fozia Fasil（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829330" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829330" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829330" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="Fozia Fasil" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829330" class="wp-caption-text"> “叛徒”中的Fozia：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在对阵莱昂的指甲决赛中，弗齐亚是死亡比赛结束时最后一位站在死亡比赛结束的球员。然后，她被叛徒谋杀了。</p><p><strong>放逐：琳达·兰德斯（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829332" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829332" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829332" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors.jpg" alt="琳达" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829332" class="wp-caption-text">琳达在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>经过几天的怀疑，包括在圆桌会议上进行了几次密切的电话，琳达成为了第二次从游戏中驱逐的叛徒。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：安娜·杜克（Anna Duke）（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829726" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829726" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829726" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1.jpg" alt="安娜·杜克（Anna Duke）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829726" class="wp-caption-text">安娜在“叛徒”信用中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在夏洛特被招募为叛徒之后，她和米纳（Minah）决定安娜在城堡的时间结束，她“不再需要”。在比赛中，安娜曾被怀疑是一名叛徒，在被选为死亡比赛之后，觉得叛徒出去了。叛徒以前曾试图招募她，但她拒绝了。</p><p><strong>放逐：Alex Oleksy（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829736" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829736" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829736" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="叛徒的亚历克斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829736" class="wp-caption-text">亚历克斯在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在整个比赛中，亚历克斯大部分都在雷达下飞行，但是厨房里的评论不佳证明了他的垮台。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：丽莎·库普兰（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831243" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831243" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831243" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors.jpg" alt="叛徒的丽莎·库普兰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831243" class="wp-caption-text">丽莎在“叛徒”信用中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>叛徒认为她是一个无法撒谎的值得信赖的信徒，在经过一些尖锐的观察之后决定谋杀英国国教牧师丽莎。</p><p><strong>放逐：莱昂·杰克曼（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831242" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831242" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831242" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors.jpg" alt="莱昂叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831242" class="wp-caption-text">莱昂在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>忠实者在死亡比赛后的举止发生了变化后，对零售商店经理莱昂（Leon）感到怀疑，导致他最亲密的盟友反对他。</p><h2>谁在第四周离开？</h2><p>该节目的最后一周以相对直截了当的方式开始，残酷地谋杀和扭曲的国际象棋比赛。</p><p>仅剩两个圆桌会议，剩下的八名选手之间的紧张局势达到了历史最高的高度。然而，游戏将通过嘲笑的秘密力量将其脑海中的脑海。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：乔·斯科特（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831230" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831230" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831230" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors.jpg" alt="乔·斯科特（Joe Scott）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831230" class="wp-caption-text">乔在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studiolambert</figcaption></figure><p>乔（Joe）是该小组的非常声音的成员，经常在圆桌会议上提出想法 - 无论他们是错误的。但是，这最终与他无能为力，因为叛徒认为谋杀他将传达强烈的信息。</p><p><strong>放逐：米纳·香农（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831236" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831236" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831236" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="米亚" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831236" class="wp-caption-text">米亚在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studiolambert</figcaption></figure><p>米纳（Minah）从一开始就以叛徒的身份发挥了一场强大的比赛，并避免了很长时间的怀疑，但最终，这一切都变得脱节了。最后，叛徒夏洛特（Charlotte）将她扔到公共汽车下，进行了最后一票，这意味着她被驱逐出城堡。</p><p>被淘汰后，最后一位剩下的叛徒夏洛特（Charlotte）选择招募弗雷迪（Freddie），他勉强接受了邀请。</p><p><strong>放逐：弗雷迪·弗雷泽（Freddie Fraser）（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831608" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831608" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831608" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors.jpg" alt="弗雷迪·弗雷泽（Freddie Fraser）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831608" class="wp-caption-text">弗雷迪在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studiolambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管夏洛特欺骗了新招募的叛徒弗雷迪谋杀Leanne，但在节目的倒数第二集中没有谋杀，尽管她没有盾牌，但她无法被谋杀。通过弗雷迪（Freddie）笨拙的撒谎尝试，他被忠实的洞察力，随后被驱逐出境。</p><p>在任务中获得最多的钱后，弗朗西斯卡（Francesca）获得了先知的力量，使她能够在一次私人会议上发现一名选手的真正身份。在一个戏剧性的悬崖峭壁中，我们发现她选择揭露夏洛特。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-3-who-was-killed-3827323">本周在“叛徒”上被杀害的哨所？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
瑞士技术DJ和制片人Aldanya在癌症之后去世https://www.nme.com/news/music/swiss-techno-dj-and-producer-aldanya-dies-after-cancer-battle-3831601?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=swiss-techno-dj-and-生产者 -  aldanya-dies-ter-catter-cattle-battleLaura Molloy Thu, 23 Jan 2025 21:51:42 +0000 Music NewsNews..DanceElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3831601 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦技术场景的致敬一直在涌入</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/swiss-techno-dj-and-producer-aldanya-dies-after-cancer-battle-3831601">瑞士邮政技术DJ和制片人Aldanya在癌症战后去世，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>瑞士Techno DJ和制片人Aldanya（真名Crystal Margaret）在与癌症作斗争后死亡。</p><p>玛格丽特（Margaret）的家人证实，在与“侵略性形式的乳腺癌形式”作斗争后，她于周日（1月19日）去世。他们在对<a href="https://mixmag.net/read/swiss-techno-dj-aldanya-died-following-battle-cancer-news" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Mixmag的</em></a>一份声明中写道：“我们都伤心欲绝。”</p><p>他们继续说：“她是最善良，最慷慨，才华横溢，美丽的人，还有更多无数的品质。” “水晶留下了遗产，她受到了许多人的爱，只要我们活着，她就会在我们心中。”</p><p>玛格丽特（Margaret）首次接触音乐，始于在家，她在童年时期弹奏古典钢琴。在她十几岁的时候，她对舞蹈音乐产生了兴趣，并自学到DJ，然后在伦敦的Point Blank音乐学校学习。</p><p>玛格丽特（Margaret）开发了舞台名称Aldanya，以制作技术和室内音乐而闻名，在首都的著名场所中演奏，包括面料，Fold，Werkhaus，Willkhaus，乡村地下，热身节日和Steelyard。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Aldanya- Just Techno-与客人DJ -Riva -Riva-直播伦敦17-04-2022" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2ZA2rmAJCPE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Techno社区的致敬一直在社交媒体上涌入，折衷的动物​​园事件写作，他们“伤心欲绝”以听到这一消息。 “She will be remembered as someone who was there for everyone, someone who was caring for her friends and always expanding new ideas how to improve music industry,” they wrote. “She will be missed a lot.”</p><p> “It&#39;s a huge shock and a real tragedy, Crystal was a lovely person and a very talented DJ and producer,” Balrog, head of Khazad – a UK label that released her music – said in a statement to <em>Mixmag</em> . “She will be a massive loss to the scene. My thoughts go out to her friends and family.”</p><p> Warm Up, a London rave community, also shared a tribute to Margaret, writing: “Her infectious passion for music was always evident in her powerful performances that captured so many hearts. She was a truly beautiful human who radiated love, warmth and kindness.” DJ Ebra Al wrote: “World lost you far far too early. I love you and you will never be forgotten. Rest in music, my beautiful friend.” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFDxDOyMsPQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803