828551">to sing &#39;America the Beautiful&#39; following Trump&#39;s swearing-in ceremony</a> .</p><p> Speaking ahead of the performance, Underwood said: “I love our country and am honored to have been asked to sing at the Inauguration and to be a small part of this historic event,” per <em><a href="https://apnews.com/article/trump-inauguration-carrie-underwood-christopher-macchio-greenwood-601d590dd45b7f9544d06843f7279784" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Associated Press</a></em> . “我很谦虚地在我们必须以团结的精神并向未来聚在一起的时候接听电话。”</p><p>但是，当实际的一天到来时，它陷入了技术困难，背景轨道无法演奏，安德伍德（Underwood）不得不唱歌卡贝拉（Capella）。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Carrie Underwood sings ‘America the Beautiful’ at Trump inauguration" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/048Qw1Ii3tk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>现在，乡村音乐歌手Jason Aldean已经为她提供了辩护。 Speaking to <em>Fox and Friends</em> , Aldean said: “First of all, it&#39;s a hard song to do anyway. When you&#39;re supposed to be singing to a track and that&#39;s what gives you pitch reference for the song and to not have that and for her to just kinda say, &#39;All right, listen, we&#39;ll go.&#39;这是一个很大的举动，这是她的职业动作，所以我认为这很棒。”</p><p>黑社会在整个职业生涯中保持了她的政治观点，但仍因与特朗普的联系而受到批评。 She also didn&#39;t endorse a candidate for the presidential election in November.</p><p>奥尔德（Aldean）还分享了他对艺术家对自己的政治观点的挺身而出的想法，并告诉电台：“我确实感到有些证明。 My wife and I talk about this all the time, for the last four years especially, you&#39;re taking a lot of heat for stepping out and telling people how we feel about the state of the country and that regime that had been in office. It&#39;s been a little odd at times.”</p><p>安德伍德（Underwood）宣布她将在活动中表演时受到抨击。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/whoopi-goldberg-defends-carrie-underwood-over-trump-inauguration-performance-but-says-she-wont-be-watching-3829309">Whoopi Goldberg later defended her decision</a> , but added that she will not be watching. </p><figure id="attachment_3827845" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827845" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827845" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="唐纳德·特朗普" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_donaldtrump_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827845" class="wp-caption-text">当选总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在华盛顿特区的国会大厦山（DC</figcaption></figure><p> The actor and chat show host has been critical of Trump&#39;s policies in the past – even <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/whoopi-goldberg-refuses-to-say-donald-trump-name-on-air-following-election-win-3810687">refusing to say his name after his election win</a> .</p><p> Also performing at the Donald Trump inauguration events were <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-criticised-for-playing-donald-trumps-crypto-ball-a-bridge-too-far-3830116">Snoop Dogg</a> and Soulja Boy, who performed at the Crypto Ball, and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nelly-defends-playing-donald-trumps-inauguration-im-doing-this-because-its-an-honour-3830192">Nelly, who responded to backlash, calling it “an honour” to perform at the ceremony</a> .</p><p> <a href