Kid Rock）于2023年11月11日在麦迪逊广场花园（Madison Square Garden）的UFC 295在纽约市。 （Chris Unger/Zuffa LLC的照片通过Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">Ariana Grande</a> has also <a href="https://www.instagram.com/stories/arianagrande/3549916426321198595/">shared a repost on Instagram Stories that reads</a> : “Let&#39;s be very clear: queer and trans people were here before Donald Trump and will continued to be here after he&#39;s dead.您是否想让我们存在是我们这样做的简单事实的次要的。太阳不在乎您是否签署一项行政命令，告诉它每天早晨停止上升。它只是继续上升。”</p><p> During the inauguration events, Elon Musk gave a speech expressing his delight at Trump&#39;s victory, before <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">slapping his chest with his right hand and extending his arm diagonally upwards with the palm facing down</a> .然后，X/Twitter所有者转过身向讲台后面的人群成员转身，重复了手势。</p><p> Many people have compared the gesture to a Nazi salute, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-frank-iero-calls-out-elon-musk-controversial-salute-3830992">including My Chemical Romance&#39;s Frank Iero</a> , who wrote: “Fuck this guy and every single person supporting this shit or wasting any kind of breath attempting to defend it,” he wrote in the caption,在添加之前：“您的真颜色正在闪耀。 #smashhate。”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jason-aldean-calls-carrie-underwood-a-pro-for-performing-amid-tech-issues-at-donald-trumps-inauguration-3831586">Jason Aldean calls Carrie Underwood a “pro” for performing amid tech issues at Donald Trump&#39;s inauguration</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
